#RESUME_CUSTOM_OVERVIEW="Design systems engineer specializing in component libraries, web components, and the developer experience that drives adoption. I make architectural decisions, mentor engineers, and shape how teams build with design tokens, Storybook, and accessibility standards like WCAG. At Alaska Airlines, I automated a manual, repo-by-repo release process across 20+ repositories. At E*TRADE, I was part of the team building accessible web components with Stencil for data-dense financial interfaces. 10+ years across React, Vue, Svelte, TypeScript, and CI/CD."
