RESUME_CUSTOM_OVERVIEW="Frontend engineer who shapes how product teams build and ship at scale. I define technical standards, lead design system strategy, and mentor engineers on architecture and developer experience. At Alaska Airlines, I eliminated a manual, repo-by-repo release process across 20+ component repositories. At E*TRADE, I contributed to a design system serving dozens of product teams, building accessible web components and cutting deploy time from a full day to under 3 hours. 10+ years across React, Vue, Svelte, web components, TypeScript, and CI/CD."
